text: Kassandra Ndoutou Eboa Missipo (born 3 February 1998) is a Belgian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Super League Vrouwenvoetbal club RSC Anderlecht the Belgium women's national team. ==Career== Missipo has been capped for the Belgium national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==Personal life== Missipo is of Cameroonian descent and openly lesbian. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian women's footballers Category:Belgium women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Belgian people of Cameroonian descent Category:Sportspeople from Flemish Brabant Category:People from Asse Category:Lesbian sportswomen Category:LGBT association football players Category:LGBT sportspeople from Belgium
title: Kassandra Missipo
